police have arrived.

106
00:06:15,739 --> 00:06:16,672
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): Police?

107
00:06:16,705 --> 00:06:18,039
NEWSCASTER: They're
a welcome sight

108
00:06:18,072 --> 00:06:19,105
