much more suspicious.

122
00:06:44,239 --> 00:06:46,439
NEWSCASTER: The police are
coming out of the building.

123
00:06:46,472 --> 00:06:48,005
They've secured the area.

124
00:06:50,572 --> 00:06:52,039
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): Where is he?

125
00:06:52,072 --> 00:06:54,572
