169
00:09:39,172 --> 00:09:41,339
-I've a couple of
exams coming up.

170
00:09:41,372 --> 00:09:42,705
-I see.

171
00:09:42,739 --> 00:09:44,839
Well, don't push
yourself too hard, OK?

172
00:09:44,872 --> 00:09:45,472
-Kay.

173
00:09:45,505 --> 00:09:46,039
You too, dad.

174
00:10:05,939 --> 00:10:08,539
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): I wouldn't be
surprised if one of the others

