190
00:10:46,405 --> 00:10:47,505
NEAR: Yes?

191
00:10:47,539 --> 00:10:49,172
This is Near.

192
00:10:49,205 --> 00:10:51,305
AIZAWA: I'm with the
Japanese task force.

193
00:10:51,339 --> 00:10:52,039
My name is Aizawa.

194
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:11,710
MISA: So, the time
has finally come.

195
00:11:11,743 --> 00:11:13,743
If I do this my
safety is guaranteed,

196
00:11:13,777 --> 00:11:16,710
and I can finally just
to be a normal wife.

197
00:11:16,743 --> 00:11:18,443
This is what Light wants for me.

198
00:11:18,477 --> 00:11:22,243
He wants me to be happy,
just as a woman should be.

199
00:11:22,277 --> 00:11:23,943
Thank you, Light.

200
00:11:27,577 --> 00:11:28,377
