possible explanation.

251
00:13:27,710 --> 00:13:29,210
Why else would the
deputy director

252
00:13:29,243 --> 00:13:33,110
say he would kill
Kira, and then himself?

253
00:13:33,143 --> 00:13:35,410
Therefore, tha
tmeans the second L,

254
00:13:35,443 --> 00:13:39,843
and hte person I think is
Kira, can only be one man.

255
00:13:39,877 --> 00:13:40,377
Light Yagami.

256
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:52,443
AIZAWA: Light.

257
00:13:52,477 --> 00:13:53,510
-Yes?

258
00:13:53,543 --> 00:13:55,243
-There's something
you should know.

259
00:13:55,277 --> 00:13:57,277
I phoned Near and talked to him.

260
00:14:02,477 --> 00:14:03,977
-Don't worry about it.

261
00:14:04,010 --> 00:14:06,543
After all, I was the
one who recommended it.

262
00:14:06,577 --> 00:14:10,210
So, what did the two of
you end up discussing?

263
00:14:10,243 --> 00:14:12,277
No, on second thought, I
probably shouldn't ask.

264
00:14:12,310 --> 00:14:13,843
I guess it's not
appropriate for me

265
00:14:13,877 --> 00:14:16,477
to ask those kinds of
questions if I'm a suspect.

266
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:18,577
-Hm.

267
00:14:18,610 --> 00:14:19,643
Don't get me wrong.

268
00:14:19,677 --> 00:14:21,643
I want to believe
that you aren't Kira,

269
00:14:21,677 --> 00:14:22,777
but I've got to be certain.

270
00:14:22,810 --> 00:14:24,410
I'm sorry to have
to do this again,

271
00:14:24,443 --> 00:14:26,077
but I want to put you
under surveillance

272
00:14:26,110 --> 00:14:27,843
until we catch Kira.

273
00:14:27,877 --> 00:14:30,710
I'm afraid that goes
for Misa Amane as well.

274
00:14:30,743 --> 00:14:32,910
I'm going to search
your place right now.

275
00:14:32,943 --> 00:14:35,977
There's a possibility that
Amane might have a notebook.

276
00:14:36,010 --> 00:14:37,910
-Hang on a second, Aizawa!

277
00:14:37,943 --> 00:14:38,643
-No.

278
00:14:38,677 --> 00:14:39,377
Go right ahead.

279
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:40,410
Look at this way.

280
00:14:40,443 --> 00:14:41,877
At least you can
prove to everyone

281
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:44,610
that I'm not sneaking around
and contacting Misa in private,

282
00:14:44,643 --> 00:14:45,110
right?

283
00:14:57,943 --> 00:14:59,710
-Huh?

284
00:14:59,743 --> 00:15:00,910
Mogi?

285
00:15:00,943 --> 00:15:01,777
-I'm coming with you.

286
00:15:01,810 --> 00:15:03,143
I want to make sure, too.

287
00:15:08,543 --> 00:15:11,610
-It would be best for
everyone if Light wasn't Kira.

288
00:15:11,643 --> 00:15:13,777
But if Amane has any
evidence on her that

289
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:15,643
connects her with Kira, then--

290
00:15:24,977 --> 00:15:27,343
[doorbell]

291
00:15:43,643 --> 00:15:44,743
-Huh?

292
00:15:44,777 --> 00:15:49,243
-Motchi, Monchichi, long
time no see, you two!

293
00:15:49,277 --> 00:15:51,643
Light hasn't been
home at all lately,

294
00:15:51,677 --> 00:15:53,577
so I've been super bored.

295
00:15:53,610 --> 00:15:54,810
-Uh--

296
00:15:54,843 --> 00:15:56,943
-Well, there's no way she's
got the notebook hidden

297
00:15:56,977 --> 00:15:58,343
under a dress like that.

298
00:15:58,377 --> 00:15:59,877
-We were just
investigating a tip

299
00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,910
that there were explosives
planted in L's house.

300
00:16:01,943 --> 00:16:04,410
We think it's a prank, but we'd
like to check the rooms, just

301
00:16:04,443 --> 00:16:05,477
in case.

302
00:16:05,510 --> 00:16:06,043
-What?

303
00:16:06,077 --> 00:16:06,643
How about Light?

304
00:16:06,677 --> 00:16:07,443
Is he OK?

305
00:16:07,477 --> 00:16:08,377
I have to call him.

306
00:16:08,410 --> 00:16:09,277
-No.

307
00:16:09,310 --> 00:16:10,443
You can't call him right now.

308
00:16:10,477 --> 00:16:11,543
-How come?

309
00:16:11,577 --> 00:16:12,677
-Don't worry.

310
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:14,310
Light's safe, but he's
really busy right now.

311
00:16:14,343 --> 00:16:15,910
He has some other
things he has to do,

312
00:16:15,943 --> 00:16:19,077
so he's handed the investigation
over to us for the time being.

313
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:20,510
-Oh, I get it.

314
00:16:20,543 --> 00:16:22,243
Light loves me like
crazy, so he doesn't

315
00:16:22,277 --> 00:16:23,910
want me to call him,
'cause that'll only

316
00:16:23,943 --> 00:16:26,277
make him worry about me.

317
00:16:26,310 --> 00:16:30,077
-(VOICEOVER) Search as
much as you like, Aizawa.

318
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,443
You won't find the notebook.

319
00:16:36,510 --> 00:16:37,843
[yawn]

320
00:16:42,177 --> 00:16:43,577
-I wouldn't like
all the suspicion

321
00:16:43,610 --> 00:16:45,543
to ruin the atmosphere
around here.

322
00:16:45,577 --> 00:16:47,510
-This isn't a social club.

323
00:16:47,543 --> 00:16:49,910
I think Aizawa and Mogi
should do as they see fit.

324
00:16:52,143 --> 00:16:53,377
-It's time for Kira's Kingdom.

325
00:17:02,077 --> 00:17:05,110
-Greetings to all my
fellow Kira worshippers.

326
00:17:05,143 --> 00:17:08,810
I am Demegawa, the
voice of our god, Kira.

327
00:17:08,843 --> 00:17:09,810
Behold!

328
00:17:09,843 --> 00:17:11,843
This is the new
Kira's Kingdom, which

329
00:17:11,877 --> 00:17:14,043
shares its name
with this program.

330
00:17:14,077 --> 00:17:15,977
Its construction
is going smoothly,

331
00:17:16,010 --> 00:17:19,343
but will depend on the generous
support of our loyal viewers.

332
00:17:19,377 --> 00:17:24,243
Once it has been completed,
let us welcome our god here!

333
00:17:24,277 --> 00:17:24,943
-Whoa.

334
00:17:24,977 --> 00:17:26,043
Talk about bad taste.

335
00:17:32,477 --> 00:17:34,577
-Hey, so is everything OK?

336
00:17:34,610 --> 00:17:35,410
-Oh, yeah.

337
00:17:35,443 --> 00:17:36,943
Seems like it was just a prank.

338
00:17:36,977 --> 00:17:38,210
-Oh.

339
00:17:38,243 --> 00:17:39,743
-But just in case, one of
us is going to stay and keep

340
00:17:39,777 --> 00:17:41,477
watch over you for
the next few days.

341
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:42,177
-Really?

342
00:17:42,210 --> 00:17:43,477
Oh, that would be great.

343
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:46,243
Mogi, why don't you go
back to headquarters?

344
00:17:46,277 --> 00:17:47,610
I'll say on guard here.

345
00:17:47,643 --> 00:17:48,610
-Huh?

346
00:17:48,643 --> 00:17:51,010
I'm with Monchichi
instead of Motchi?

347
00:17:51,043 --> 00:17:51,677
-What's wrong?

348
00:17:51,710 --> 00:17:52,843
Don't you trust me?

349
00:17:52,877 --> 00:17:54,110
-No.

350
00:17:54,143 --> 00:17:56,177
You're just not Monchichi
without your old haircut.

351
00:17:56,210 --> 00:17:57,810
You're not cute anymore.

352
00:17:57,843 --> 00:17:59,310
[laughter]

353
00:17:59,343 --> 00:18:00,043
-Mogi!

354
00:18:00,077 --> 00:18:01,410
-Yes, sir. my apologies.

355
00:18:01,443 --> 00:18:02,010
-All right.

356
00:18:02,043 --> 00:18:04,443
You stay.

357
00:18:04,477 --> 00:18:07,810
-We are now accepting donations,
starting at the million yen

358
00:18:07,843 --> 00:18:10,477
mark towards the completion
of Kira's Kingdom.

359
00:18:10,510 --> 00:18:12,043
So, if you truly--

360
00:18:12,077 --> 00:18:13,043
-This sounds like a con.

361
00:18:13,077 --> 00:18:13,877
-Yep.

362
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:16,843
Just another scam at this point.

363
00:18:16,877 --> 00:18:19,910
-It doesn't even seem
like Kira's style.

364
00:18:19,943 --> 00:18:21,177
-(VOICEOVER) Demegawa.

365
00:18:21,210 --> 00:18:23,177
He's just acting on his own now.

366
00:18:23,210 --> 00:18:24,677
If he keeps doing
this, he'll end up

367
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:27,577
pushing people away from Kira.

368
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:29,077
I don't need him anymore.

369
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:31,043
But I can't do
much at the moment.

370
00:18:36,243 --> 00:18:36,910
-Hey.

371
00:18:36,943 --> 00:18:37,577
Welcome back, Aizawa.

372
00:18:40,410 --> 00:18:43,577
-We didn't find a notebook
in Light's or Misa's room.

373
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:44,510
But still--

374
00:18:44,543 --> 00:18:45,843
-I understand.

375
00:18:45,877 --> 00:18:48,310
You're more than welcome to
keep watch over Misa and I

376
00:18:48,343 --> 00:18:50,543
until you're satisfied.

377
00:18:50,577 --> 00:18:52,943
-Next on the program,
it's time for me

378
00:18:52,977 --> 00:18:55,977
to introduce the new leaders I
have chosen for Kira's Kingdom.

379
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:02,077
The first gentleman is--

380
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:02,577
-Delete.

381
00:19:07,043 --> 00:19:07,977
[gasping]

382
00:19:10,943 --> 00:19:14,177
-We will unite with
Kira, and work with him.

383
00:19:14,210 --> 00:19:14,677
-Delete!

384
00:19:19,143 --> 00:19:22,077
Delete!

385
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:22,577
Delete!

386
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:35,477
-Save me.

387
00:19:44,843 --> 00:19:45,310
-And delete.

388
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:50,643
[groan]

389
00:19:57,610 --> 00:20:00,077
-Wha-- What the hell is this?

390
00:20:00,110 --> 00:20:01,843
Why would Kira kill
his own supporters?

391
00:20:01,877 --> 00:20:03,910
-Do you think it's because
they're going overboard

392
00:20:03,943 --> 00:20:05,477
with this?

393
00:20:05,510 --> 00:20:07,577
-That might be a possibility.

394
00:20:07,610 --> 00:20:09,777
But this is horrible.

395
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:10,943
-(VOICEOVER) What's going on?

396
00:20:10,977 --> 00:20:13,443
There was no chance for
either Misa Amane or Light

397
00:20:13,477 --> 00:20:17,277
to use the notebook
to kill Demegawa.

398
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,710
LIGHT (VOICEOVER): Mikami.

399
00:20:18,743 --> 00:20:21,277
I can definitely use him.

400
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:23,610
It seems I was right
to choose him for this.

401
00:20:23,643 --> 00:20:26,777
He understands Kira's
beliefs and ideals perfectly,

402
00:20:26,810 --> 00:20:29,477
and he knows what Kira
wants and doesn't want.

403
00:20:29,510 --> 00:20:33,410
Thanks to that, he takes action
without needing my orders.

404
00:20:33,443 --> 00:20:36,243
I had Misa relinquish
ownership of the Death Note.

405
00:20:36,277 --> 00:20:38,677
Before she lost all her
memories of the notebook,

406
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:40,543
she sent it to
someone else, along

407
00:20:40,577 --> 00:20:42,843
with some special instructions.

408
00:20:42,877 --> 00:20:45,843
Now she won't be able to
answer any questions about it.

409
00:20:45,877 --> 00:20:48,677
She's just an ordinary woman.

410
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:51,977
The main problem was
selecting the next owner.

411
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:54,243
I saw him trying to speak to
Kira through the television

412
00:20:54,277 --> 00:20:55,710
broadcasts.

413
00:20:55,743 --> 00:20:58,877
It was clear he worshiped Kira
from the bottom of this heart.

414
00:20:58,910 --> 00:21:01,143
He would understand that
he was chosen simply

415
00:21:01,177 --> 00:21:02,943
by receiving and
accepting the notebook.

416
00:21:07,043 --> 00:21:10,843
There was no mistake
in my selection.

417
00:21:10,877 --> 00:21:13,210
Teru Mikami.

418
00:21:13,243 --> 00:21:17,710
He's more than worthy of
becoming the hand of Kira.

419
00:21:17,743 --> 00:21:18,577
-Shinigami.

420
00:21:18,610 --> 00:21:20,610
Thank you for coming to me.

421
00:21:20,643 --> 00:21:22,943
Now I'll be able to punish
evildoers with death.

422
00:21:27,843 --> 00:21:30,777
[laughter] God.

423
00:21:39,255 --> 00:21:42,688
[theme music]

424
00:22:50,354 --> 00:22:53,354
LIGHT: You're a woman who the
entire world pays attention to.

425
00:22:53,388 --> 00:22:56,288
It must be fate for us to
cross paths again like this.

426
00:22:56,321 --> 00:22:59,554
Please, just listen to what I
have to say first, all right?

427
00:22:59,588 --> 00:23:00,421
Let's meet somewhere.

428
00:23:00,454 --> 00:23:01,954
Alone.

